# Load Testing Project Dashboard – Development Requirements

## Objective

Develop a modern, visually appealing, and interactive web application that serves as a centralized dashboard for the Load Testing Project. The dashboard should provide complete visibility into all load-testing assets, including JMeter scripts, test data files, execution reports, project structure, and execution history, all accessible from a single interface.

