# Dashboard Features

## 1. Home Dashboard

Create a modern landing page displaying:

* Total JMeter Scripts
* Total Test Data Files
* Total Reports Available
* Latest Execution Details
* Project Health Overview
* Quick Navigation Cards
* Interactive Statistics and Charts

Use a professional UI with:

* Responsive Design
* Dark/Light Theme Support
* Glassmorphism or Modern Dashboard Styling
* Interactive Cards
* Smooth Animations
* Search and Filter Functionality

---

## 2. Project Structure Explorer

Display the complete project structure in a collapsible tree view similar to:

Project Root
│
├── JMX Scripts
│ └── BTC_USSD_LOADINFTESTING_0TPS.jmx
│
├── TestData
│ ├── File1.csv
│ ├── File2.csv
│ └── ...
│
├── Reports
│ ├── Report_1
│ ├── Report_2
│ └── ...
│
└── Other Resources

Features:

* Expand/Collapse folders
* File counts
* Search files
* File metadata
* Download/View options

---

## 3. JMeter Script Management

Display:

* Script Name
* Script Location
* Last Modified Date
* Number of Thread Groups
* Number of Requests
* Referenced CSV Files
* Description

Provide:

* View Script
* Download Script
* Dependency Mapping

---

## 4. Test Data Repository

Display all CSV files available under the TestData folder.

For each CSV:

* File Name
* File Size
* Row Count
* Column Count
* Last Modified Date

Include:

* CSV Preview
* Search Records
* Sort Columns
* Download Option
* Data Statistics

Display relationships between:

CSV File → JMX Script → Reports

---

## 5. Reports Dashboard

Automatically fetch reports from the reportPath directory.

Display:

* Report Name
* Execution Date
* Duration
* TPS
* Error Percentage
* Pass/Fail Status

Include visualizations:

* Response Time Trends
* TPS Graphs
* Error Trends
* Throughput Analysis
* Execution Comparison Charts

---

## 6. Dependency Mapping

Create a visual flow diagram showing:

Test Data Files
↓
JMeter Scripts
↓
Execution Reports

Users should easily understand:

* Which CSV files are used by which scripts
* Which reports were generated from which scripts

---

## 7. Search Center

Global search across:

* Scripts
* CSV Files
* Reports
* Folder Structure

Provide:

* Advanced Filters
* Quick Navigation
* File Location Tracking

