# User Roles


## Admin Portal

Admin users should be able to:

* Upload JMX Scripts
* Upload CSV Files
* Upload Reports
* Edit Metadata
* Manage Users
* Manage Dashboard Settings
* Generate Summary Reports
* Configure Project Information

Admin Dashboard should include:

* Activity Logs
* Upload History
* User Management
* System Health

---

## User Portal

Read-only access:

* View Scripts
* View CSV Files
* View Reports
* Download Authorized Files
* Search Assets
* View Analytics

Users should not be allowed to modify project content.

---

# Database Requirement

Use Microsoft Excel as the backend data repository.

Create structured sheets for:

## Users

* User ID
* Name
* Email
* Role
* Status

## Scripts

* Script Name
* Path
* Description
* Last Updated

## Test Data

* File Name
* Path
* Row Count
* Column Count

## Reports

* Report Name
* Execution Date
* Metrics

The application should read and update Excel dynamically.

